channel.description:
READ THE POST BEFORE POSTING!
Help, I can't get my server online maybe the problem is this: [IMG]http://i138.photobucket.com/albums/q248/hakkuari/moparerror.jpg[/img] There's nothing on the dns part and btw the languange is finnish. The ip address 192.168.0.100 works only for me.
I already know the no-ip, portforwarding and runserver.bat things. The server worked fine before we moved into different city.
But, if you know some portforwarding tips then, your free to post em.
